13
00:01:54,360 --> 00:01:57,113
Thank you very much. Take care.
非常感谢，保重。

15
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,194
Taxi!
出租车！

19
00:02:49,446 --> 00:02:54,599
Oh, my God! Oh, my God!
噢，我的天呐！噢，我的天呐！

20
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:01,357
I missed you. Oh, no...
我想死你了，哦，不对...

27
00:03:16,040 --> 00:03:17,758
I'm getting married tomorrow.
我明天就要结婚了。

28
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:18,989
I'm so glad you're here,
你们能来我好高兴啊，

29
00:03:19,080 --> 00:03:23,631
because I have a secret and I can't tell anybody else.
因为我有一个不能告诉其他人的秘密

31
00:03:28,640 --> 00:03:30,676
I've invited my dad to my wedding.
我请了我爸爸来参加我的婚礼。

32
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,392
You are joking!
你在说笑！

33
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:33,737
You found him at last?
你终于找到他了？

40
00:03:57,480 --> 00:04:00,153
It's the diary she kept the year she was pregnant with me.
是她怀上我那年的日记。

43
00:04:06,640 --> 00:04:08,756
I don't know if I want to hear this!  I do!
我都不知道自己要不要听这个呢！   我要！

73
00:05:30,238 --> 00:05:31,879
The plot thickens.
没那么简单。

93
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:25,635
God! Stop growing!
上帝！别再长大了！

107
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:14,239
So, who is your dad?
那么，谁才是你爸爸？

126
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:23,599
Bride or groom?
新娘还是新郎？

127
00:08:24,080 --> 00:08:26,913
Bride, although I've actually never met her.
新娘，不过我跟她还素未谋面。

132
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:45,351
Mother? We're the same age.
母亲？我们是同龄人。

134
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:52,554
Sailor.
水手。

135
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:55,588
No.
不。

142
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:33,950
I want the perfect wedding, and I want my father to give me away.
我要一个完美的婚礼，我要我的父亲将我托付出去。

144
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:38,799
I will know my father as soon as I see him.
谁是我的父亲我一看就知道。

146
00:09:42,640 --> 00:09:44,392
Put me down. I'm getting married tomorrow.
放倒我吧。我明天就要结婚了。

147
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:45,754
Please be careful.
请注意了。

154
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:59,836
You make me sound so unromantic!
你说得我好像一点都不懂浪漫似的！

155
00:09:59,920 --> 00:10:01,717
I just thought we should save our money for travelling.
我只想把钱存下来好去旅行。

158
00:10:06,560 --> 00:10:08,437
I'm just getting some props for tonight.
我只是为了晚上的活动上来拿些装备.

159
00:10:09,640 --> 00:10:11,915
For his bachelor party.
为了他的单身汉晚会。

161
00:10:17,280 --> 00:10:19,430
Because he would say that I'd have to tell my mom.
因为他会让我告诉我妈的。

163
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:24,398
By the time she finds out, it'll be too late.
当她知道的时候，已经太迟了。

164
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:28,393
I feel like there's a part of me missing,
我总觉得我的生命不完整，

168
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:48,799
That's good.
很好。

170
00:10:59,920 --> 00:11:01,638
Come on, Cleopatra.
快点，埃及艳后。

171
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:09,949
My shoe!
我的鞋！

172
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:17,033
Will you look at what the tide washed in?
你们瞧瞧海浪都把什么冲来了啊？

175
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:38,351
Look at you!
瞧瞧你！

176
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:40,590
You baby!         Look at you!
你这个宝贝！  瞧瞧你！

177
00:11:40,680 --> 00:11:41,954
You look fantastic!
你看起来真美极了！

178
00:11:42,040 --> 00:11:43,189
You look like an old hippie!
你看起来像老嬉皮士！

179
00:11:43,280 --> 00:11:44,998
She looks fab.
她很靓。

185
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:05,150
So, any men at this wedding?
对了，这次婚礼有男人吗？

188
00:12:10,880 --> 00:12:14,509
No! Not for me, for her!
不！我不要，给她吧！

191
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:24,268
mushrooms? Various vegetables?
蘑菇？各种各样的蔬菜？

192
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:26,157
It's time to find Mr Right!
是时候该有个真命天子了！

193
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:29,152
Oh, please. Boring!
啊，饶了我吧。无聊！

199
00:12:48,520 --> 00:12:52,957
You know, I do not know what is going on in that child's head sometimes.
听我说，我有时候根本不知道那孩子都想些什么。

202
00:12:58,520 --> 00:13:00,511
Sometimes I think they'll never leave.
有时候我还以为他们永远也不想离开呢。

205
00:13:05,520 --> 00:13:06,509
Of course not!
当然不想啊！

208
00:13:13,760 --> 00:13:15,557
He's the leading man at tomorrow's shindig.
他就是明天狂欢的那个男主角。

209
00:13:15,640 --> 00:13:17,198
The lucky man.
那个幸运的家伙。

228
00:14:15,480 --> 00:14:17,994
You should have brought the iron lung.
你应该把你的铁肺带来的。

229
00:14:18,120 --> 00:14:20,475
Why did I wear stilettos?
为什么我要穿高跟鞋？

235
00:14:41,800 --> 00:14:43,394
I bet you don't remember me.
我打赌你不记得我了。

238
00:14:51,160 --> 00:14:52,195
Look at my baby,
瞧瞧我的宝贝，

240
00:14:54,920 --> 00:14:59,948
Oh, please, I'm getting married. I'm not joining a convent!
噢，饶了我吧，我要结婚，不要进修道院！

241
00:15:00,040 --> 00:15:01,951
She's feisty. I love that.
她很有活力，我喜欢。

242
00:15:02,040 --> 00:15:04,235
She's a chip off the old block.
有其母必有其女。

243
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:08,037
If she were more like me, she wouldn't be getting married at 20.
要是她更像我的话，她就不会20岁就结婚了。

248
00:15:17,880 --> 00:15:20,713
they would figure out a machine that would make the beds.
他们或许能造出一架整理床的机器。

250
00:15:24,400 --> 00:15:25,958
I know you, Mom.
我了解你，妈妈。

253
00:15:33,080 --> 00:15:34,399
I'm designing a website.
我正在设计一个网站。

254
00:15:34,480 --> 00:15:37,253
I just think this place has so much potential,
我只是想这个地方有这么多的潜力，

263
00:15:58,960 --> 00:16:01,349
I thought you didn't want boatloads of tourists.
我以为你不想要满载的游客呢。

269
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:20,349
Nothing works around here, except for me.
这里没什么能用的了，除了我。

271
00:16:24,600 --> 00:16:25,794
Oh, my God! Sorry.
噢，我的天！抱歉。

322
00:19:13,880 --> 00:19:15,871
What's going on?
怎么了？

323
00:19:16,240 --> 00:19:17,639
Do you feel it?
你们感觉到了吗？

324
00:19:17,720 --> 00:19:20,518
The earth moved, darling. We're falling apart here.
刚才地动了一下，亲爱的。我们差点就掉下去了。

325
00:19:20,600 --> 00:19:23,592
Don't think about it, come on. Let's go have fun.
别想了，走。我们快活去。

331
00:19:44,378 --> 00:19:45,675
Listen to this.
听听这个。

335
00:19:53,400 --> 00:19:54,799
You're just jealous.
你不就是嫉妒我嘛。

337
00:19:57,080 --> 00:19:58,593
Tell you, that's the price you have to pay
告诉你，那是你应付的代价

341
00:20:08,560 --> 00:20:10,471
Sure, we're here for the wedding.
当然，我们来参加婚礼的。

345
00:20:23,680 --> 00:20:25,398
You are expecting us?
你在等我们吗？

353
00:20:44,960 --> 00:20:48,111
Would you mind if we see our rooms before we see your mother?
你介意我们在去见你母亲之前先看看我们的房间吗？

356
00:20:51,800 --> 00:20:55,156
No! No! I mean, yes,
不行！不行！我是说，可以，

357
00:20:55,240 --> 00:20:56,753
but come this way.
但得走这边。

358
00:21:09,920 --> 00:21:10,909
Come on!
来啊！

360
00:21:17,880 --> 00:21:20,713
I got a crack in my courtyard. I gotta go fix it.
院子里有个裂缝。我得补好它。

362
00:21:23,840 --> 00:21:24,875
Sit down!
坐下！

373
00:21:47,880 --> 00:21:50,030
I don't need to be taken care of.
我不需要被人照顾。

374
00:21:50,120 --> 00:21:52,634
Yeah, but are you being taken care of?
是吗，但你不是一直被人照顾着吗？

381
00:22:15,600 --> 00:22:17,830
I do not miss it at all.
我一点也不怀念。

386
00:22:48,112 --> 00:22:49,639
but might I be shown my room now?
但是能带我去我的房间了吗?

389
00:22:55,600 --> 00:22:57,272
I sent the invites.
是我发的请柬。

390
00:22:57,800 --> 00:22:59,711
My mom doesn't know anything.
我妈对此毫不知情。

398
00:23:18,640 --> 00:23:20,437
she said she never wanted to see me again.
她说过永远也不想再见到我了。

399
00:23:20,520 --> 00:23:24,433
That was years ago. Please, it would mean a lot to me.
那是多少年前的事了啊，拜托，这对我来说意义重大。

402
00:23:30,200 --> 00:23:31,553
Good idea.         Nope.
好主意。            不成。

404
00:23:34,320 --> 00:23:35,992
It's good for you.
对你有好处。

411
00:23:55,960 --> 00:23:58,394
I'm glad my boys haven't met you. They'd never recover.
真高兴我的儿子们没碰到你。他们会无可救药的。

412
00:23:58,480 --> 00:24:00,357
You have sons?         Yes, two.
你有儿子？         是啊，两个。

417
00:24:18,520 --> 00:24:19,873
I'm going to go. Please stay.
我得走了。请别出去。

418
00:24:19,960 --> 00:24:23,794
Promise me that you'll not tell anybody that I invited you.
答应我你们不会告诉任何人是我请你们来的。

464
00:27:32,840 --> 00:27:35,559
I'd better be dreaming. You'd better not be here.
我最好是在做梦。你们最好不在这里。

467
00:27:42,920 --> 00:27:45,195
You probably don't recognise me, do you?
你很可能认不出我来了吧？

469
00:27:49,800 --> 00:27:52,519
I probably changed a bit, but you certainly haven't.
我肯能有些改变了，但你明显没有。

471
00:27:57,240 --> 00:27:58,798
I'm writing a travel piece.
我在写游记。

472
00:27:58,880 --> 00:28:00,757
I'm here on a spontaneous holiday.
我自发地来这度假的。

477
00:28:14,480 --> 00:28:15,708
Strangers?
陌生人？

478
00:28:16,560 --> 00:28:18,488
You don't know each other?
你们彼此不认识吗？

483
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:28,832
Well, she spoke Greek.
嗯，她说的希腊语。

494
00:28:52,520 --> 00:28:54,158
What about you?
那你呢？

495
00:28:54,240 --> 00:28:56,356
Just wanted to see the island.
只是想来看看这座岛。

496
00:28:56,840 --> 00:28:58,956
You know what it meant to me.
你知道它对我意味著什么。

497
00:29:01,040 --> 00:29:04,112
Okay, I'm gonna arrange for a boat
好吧，我要去准备一条船

503
00:29:14,760 --> 00:29:16,478
It's good to see you.
能见到你真好。

508
00:29:32,920 --> 00:29:35,878
I think she went down to the beach.         What's up?
我想她在海滩吧。          出什么事了？

540
00:32:41,720 --> 00:32:44,871
I'm not sure that it was him,
我不能肯定是他，

543
00:32:53,680 --> 00:32:54,999
Why didn't you tell us?
你之前为什么不告诉我们?

552
00:33:19,240 --> 00:33:21,470
Wait a minute! Don't let them hear you!
等下！别让他们听到了！

553
00:33:23,120 --> 00:33:25,350
There's no one here.         Are you sure?
这里没人啊。  你肯定吗？

554
00:33:25,440 --> 00:33:26,839
Of course I'm sure!
我当然肯定啦！

559
00:33:36,640 --> 00:33:38,312
They must've gone back to their boat.
他们肯定回自己船上去了。

561
00:33:41,040 --> 00:33:42,678
What are they doing here?
他们来这做什么啊?

568
00:34:07,840 --> 00:34:09,990
It doesn't matter about me.
对我没什么影响。

578
00:34:39,320 --> 00:34:41,629
Don't you sound like your mother?
你不觉得你的口气好像你母亲吗？

586
00:35:01,080 --> 00:35:03,550
Screw them if they can't take a joke.
要是他们开不起玩笑的话就甩了他们。

630
00:39:03,880 --> 00:39:06,348
We're gonna sail around the island. You wanna come?
我们绕岛航行。你想去吗？

631
00:39:06,440 --> 00:39:08,635
You promised you'd come to my wedding.
你们答应我要参加我的婚礼的。

633
00:39:11,960 --> 00:39:13,951
She thought we'd better get out of her hair.
她想让我们别给她添麻烦。

638
00:39:26,120 --> 00:39:27,997
She'll be so happy tomorrow.         You think so?
她明天就会很开心了。   你是这么想的吗？

639
00:39:30,120 --> 00:39:32,300
You took Mom's guitar!
你拿了妈妈的吉他？

640
00:39:32,300 --> 00:39:34,113
No, no. I borrowed it. Look.
不，不。我借的。瞧。

641
00:39:35,040 --> 00:39:36,314
No, where is it?
不，在哪呢？

649
00:39:49,880 --> 00:39:51,632
Your mother knew quite a rebel.
你母亲认识的是一个相当反叛的人。

650
00:39:51,720 --> 00:39:54,473
I was studying in Paris when I met her.
碰到她的时候我正在巴黎进修。

651
00:39:56,120 --> 00:39:59,396
I hopped on a train and followed her to Greece,
我跳上了火车跟踪她来到希腊，

695
00:42:48,040 --> 00:42:49,678
Where've you been?
你去哪里了？

696
00:42:50,040 --> 00:42:52,793
People have been arriving all afternoon. No one's seen you.
客人整个下午不断抵达。没有人看到过你。

697
00:42:52,880 --> 00:42:55,394
I'm sorry, I was around the island, I just...
对不起，我在岛上转了转，我只是...

698
00:42:55,480 --> 00:42:57,550
I just lost track of time.
忘记了时间。

700
00:43:02,440 --> 00:43:04,351
My last night of freedom.
我自由身的最后一晚。

703
00:43:14,800 --> 00:43:17,075
You know how I said I wanted to find my father?
你记得我说过要找到我的父亲吗？

705
00:43:19,520 --> 00:43:21,715
You don't need a father, you have a family.
你不需要一个父亲，你有一个家庭。

707
00:43:23,520 --> 00:43:27,628
Are you kidding? You have turned my world upside down.
你开什么玩笑？是你颠覆了我的世界。

805
00:50:10,400 --> 00:50:12,311
Really.         Good idea. Good idea.
真的。              好主意。好主意。

810
00:50:25,080 --> 00:50:26,991
Is that really your dream?
那真的是你的梦想吗？

812
00:50:29,080 --> 00:50:31,071
She just can't do it by herself.
她一个人做不下去的。

818
00:50:42,760 --> 00:50:44,716
What's your mother said about me?
你妈都跟你说了我什么吗？

820
00:50:49,520 --> 00:50:51,238
What am I doing here?
那我还在这里做什么？

823
00:50:59,760 --> 00:51:00,875
I bet it's my mother.
我打赌是我的母亲。

825
00:51:02,880 --> 00:51:04,871
I'm gonna go get them out of here.
我要出去把他们赶出这里。

827
00:51:09,840 --> 00:51:11,751
Help me out of these boots.
帮我把这些靴子脱掉。

832
00:51:24,280 --> 00:51:26,635
Fishing? Oh, please.
钓鱼？噢，饶了我吧。

833
00:51:27,080 --> 00:51:29,674
What do you suggest we do with three men?
那你建议我们该跟三个男人做什么？

844
00:52:09,240 --> 00:52:11,754
Is your father here?         I don't know.
你的父亲在这里吗？  我不知道。

845
00:52:14,480 --> 00:52:16,471
I don't know who my father is.
我不知道谁是我的父亲。

848
00:52:25,320 --> 00:52:26,958
This is fantastic!
真是棒极了！

854
00:52:40,200 --> 00:52:41,394
I guess.
我猜是。

855
00:52:42,160 --> 00:52:44,993
I always heard her money was left to family.
我一直听说她把钱留给了家人。

858
00:53:02,760 --> 00:53:03,988
I'm sorry.
对不起。

866
00:53:28,240 --> 00:53:29,878
Are you my father?
你是我父亲吗？

867
00:53:30,640 --> 00:53:33,581
Yes. I think so.
是的，我想是。

871
00:53:45,480 --> 00:53:47,357
Will you give me away tomorrow?
明天你能把我托付给新郎吗？

874
00:53:59,600 --> 00:54:00,749
Oh, God.
噢，上帝。

895
00:55:24,080 --> 00:55:25,752
I know why I'm here.
我知道我为什么来这了。

897
00:55:27,738 --> 00:55:29,390
How long have you known I'm your father?
你知道我是你父亲多久了？

900
00:55:37,640 --> 00:55:39,631
So can we wait until after my wedding?
所以我们能等到我的婚礼之后吗？

901
00:55:39,720 --> 00:55:41,790
Who's giving you away tomorrow?         Nobody.
明天谁会把你托付给新郎？      没人啊。

902
00:55:41,880 --> 00:55:43,233
Wrong. I am.
错。我会。

903
00:55:43,480 --> 00:55:45,198
Our secret till then.
到那之前是我们的秘密。

907
00:55:51,680 --> 00:55:53,352
Are you okay?
你没事吧？

908
00:55:54,760 --> 00:55:55,909
I can't breathe.
我无法呼吸了。

913
00:56:07,840 --> 00:56:11,691
Oh, my God! I'm your father!
噢，我的天啊！我是你父亲！

917
00:56:17,120 --> 00:56:20,317
I won't let you down. I'll be there.
我不会让你失望的。我一定到场。

934
00:57:08,640 --> 00:57:11,362
I was tossing and turning all night.
我辗转反侧一整夜。

935
00:57:11,362 --> 00:57:14,317
Those three guys are still loose on this island.
那三个家伙现在仍然在这岛上游荡。

936
00:57:14,400 --> 00:57:15,435
We got to do something.
我们得做点什么。

938
00:57:18,960 --> 00:57:20,863
I have been tossing and turning all night.
我辗转反侧一整夜。

948
00:58:05,360 --> 00:58:07,316
No, no, no,  you first.
不，不，不，你先。

950
00:58:18,760 --> 00:58:21,593
Last night, I discovered something wonderful.
昨夜，我发现一些非常好的事情。

953
00:58:29,760 --> 00:58:32,911
Last night? You didn't know?
昨晚？你还不知道？

958
00:58:48,920 --> 00:58:51,070
All will be revealed tonight.
今晚就会真相大白了。

963
00:59:07,000 --> 00:59:08,399
You're kidding.
你在说笑。

965
00:59:12,000 --> 00:59:14,070
I don't think I can do this.
我想我做不到。

966
00:59:14,360 --> 00:59:16,430
Well, she's a wonderful girl,
没错，她是个非常好的女孩子，

971
00:59:30,120 --> 00:59:31,109
What?
什么？

972
00:59:32,680 --> 00:59:35,592
Hey, right in time for breakfast.
嘿，正好赶上早餐。

973
00:59:35,680 --> 00:59:38,353
We're serving up the works here.
我们正在忙着呢。

980
00:59:56,920 --> 00:59:59,275
You okay?         Yeah. I'm fine. I'm fine.
你还好吧？      嗯。我很好。我很好。

985
01:00:22,200 --> 01:00:24,395
You don't have to do anything.
你什么事也不用做。

1004
01:01:18,480 --> 01:01:20,391
You're supposed to be helping me.
你们本来应该帮我的。

1006
01:01:30,920 --> 01:01:33,070
I see you kept my bagpipes.
我看到你保留了我的风笛。

1008
01:01:40,520 --> 01:01:43,239
Well, you don't need bagpipes to do that.
那么，你不需要风笛也能做到。

1010
01:01:46,191 --> 01:01:48,750
This is our dream, remember?
这是我们的梦想，还记得吗？

1022
01:02:17,120 --> 01:02:18,792
She's a bright kid.
她是个聪明的孩子。

1023
01:02:18,880 --> 01:02:20,711
I know. I know.
我知道。我知道。

1024
01:02:21,200 --> 01:02:23,839
But, you know, my daughter has a mind of her own.
但是，你知道的，我女儿有自己的想法。

1025
01:02:24,160 --> 01:02:28,278
Oh, yeah. I see that. I see that.
哦，是啊。我明白了。我明白了。

1026
01:02:29,720 --> 01:02:31,631
But she's so young.         I know.
但是她还年轻。         我知道。

1027
01:02:32,080 --> 01:02:33,991
I mean, does she know what she really wants?
我指的是，她知道自己真的想要什么吗？

1031
01:02:45,000 --> 01:02:46,737
I have two grown children.
我有两个长大的孩子。

1040
01:03:04,040 --> 01:03:06,634
You know, I'm free and I'm single.
你看到了，我很自由而且还是单身。

1300
01:23:48,720 --> 01:23:50,358
I don't know.
我不知道。

1301
01:23:53,080 --> 01:23:55,389
Can you forgive me?         What?
你能原谅我吗？   什么?